text: Karabulak () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Ikryaninsky Selsoviet, Ikryaninsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 275 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 48 km from Astrakhan, 13 km from Ikryanoye. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ikryaninsky District
title: Karabulak, Astrakhan Oblast
